{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act12mini_level_act12mini_st05","storyGroup":"act12mini","storySort":5,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"","storyName":"日落已久","storyPic":"storyMainPic_level_act12mini_st05","storyInfo":"托兰收到了一些企业重要资料，而一路被卷进风波的玛恩纳找到了他。在分析出旧友刺杀莱塔尼亚宾客的野心之后，二人决定无论如何都要阻止。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"activities/act12mini/level_act12mini_st05","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"USE_ITEM","costItemType":"MATERIAL","costItemId":"STORY_REVIEW_COIN","costItemCount":1,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":[],"prev":3,"next":5,"characters":["托兰","玛恩纳","泽诺","征战骑士","切斯柏","赏金猎人"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":5},{"type":"Background","image":"31_g3_mini12_farmland","screenadapt":"showall","id":6},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":7},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","text":"","id":9},{"type":"Text","text":"父亲的信。还是老样子，让我做些正经事。你们真的想听我念？","id":10},{"type":"Text","text":"“......去庇护贫困者与落难者的确是骑士应行之道，但选择同行的伙伴时则应该更加谨慎。”","id":11},{"type":"Text","text":"“不要让你该保护的人陪你一起经受苦难，也不必长久地执着于感化恶人、集合弱者。”","id":12},{"type":"Text","text":"——听到自己被骂了，满意了吗？","id":13},{"type":"Text","text":"他并不是觉得我们在做的事情有错，只是在他眼里不会有结果罢了。","id":14},{"type":"Text","text":"“你要救活那些作物，只有先尽力翻动他们足下贫瘠的土地。”","id":15},{"type":"Dialog","id":16},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":17},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":18},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":19},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":20},{"type":"Background","image":"31_g5_mini12_village_n","screenadapt":"showall","id":21},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":22},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"$path_loop","volume":"0.6","id":23,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":24},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","text":"","id":25},{"type":"Text","text":"11月30日 11:20 P.M.","id":26},{"type":"Text","text":"茨沃涅克城外村庄","id":27},{"type":"Dialog","id":28},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":29},{"type":"Delay","time":"1.5","id":30},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":31},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"......我们这个平平无奇的小村庄，这两天倒是挺热闹的，不仅骑士团长能巡逻到这里来，贵族老爷竟然也亲自登门拜访。","id":32,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":33},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"是吧，玛恩纳阁下？","id":34,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":35},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......先给这个感染者一个安身处。他现在顶着感染者暴动事件主谋的罪名。","id":36,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_626_1#1$1","id":37},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泽诺","text":"先、先生，这里就是您说的，安全的地方......？您把我交给了赏金猎人？","id":38,"figure":"avg_npc_626_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_626_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":39},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"别怕，你又没什么钱，我们不至于打劫你。","id":40,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_626_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":41},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泽诺","text":"（不安地摸了摸脖子）","id":42,"figure":"avg_npc_626_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_626_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":43},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"既然我们的骑士老爷把你带过来，那你应该知道不少消息。","id":44,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"你有家人吗？需不需要信使给他们传个话，叫他们逃命？","id":45,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_626_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":46},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泽诺","text":"我，呃......","id":47,"figure":"avg_npc_626_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":48},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_626_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","id":49},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"-200","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":50},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_626_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":51},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"拿着，纸和笔。","id":53,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":54},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_paper1","volume":"1","id":55},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.7","id":56},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","fadetime":"1","id":57},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":58},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":59},{"type":"Delay","time":"1.5","id":60},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":61},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"再看看你，玛恩纳——喔，原来你带着剑只是为了让大骑士领那些家伙看到就心烦啊。","id":62,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","id":63},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"离开了那座城市，你反而可以连武器都不要了。","id":64,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","id":65},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......","id":66,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"想杀了你的人，光是我这儿的就能排一条长队。你已经傲慢到觉得自己随便用一根树枝就能打发所有人啦？","id":68,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","id":69},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"我现在就站在这里，他们怎么不动手？","id":70,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","id":71},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......剑拿给征战骑士调整了。我是来说正事的，托兰。","id":72,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"哎，开个玩笑。我知道你们约定明天取剑。","id":74,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"要是你这会儿还没想起来我们，那大家可就要伤心啦。","id":76,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"毕竟......你就这么去见他，可能会死在那里。","id":78,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......","id":80,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"别这么皱着眉头看我啊，这个时间突然找过来说正事，你不会是什么都没察觉到。","id":82,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":83},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......你知道什么？","id":84,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"只是有些猜测，不过我们俩应该想的差不多。","id":86,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":87},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"走吧，我们走得远一点，让这个可怜人自己安安静静地给家里写信。","id":88,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":89},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"虽然夜色这么深了，但河谷那边灯火通明的工厂还是能看见的......曾经帕伦尼斯科家族的庄园所在地，还挺值得怀念的，对吧？","id":90,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":91},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":92},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":93},{"type":"Character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1","id":94},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_coldforest","screenadapt":"showall","id":95},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":96},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"$drift_loop","volume":"0.6","id":97,"musicid":1},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":98},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","text":"","id":99},{"type":"Dialog","id":100},{"type":"Character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1","id":101},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":102},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-200","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":103},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":104},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"200","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":105},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1","fadetime":"0.7","id":106},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":107},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1","focus":"1","id":108},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"......抱歉，我看到这边有黑烟，所以赶来看看是否有火情。是不是打扰到您了？","id":109,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":110},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"没事，只是我扔了几本笔记进去，皮革的封面烧起来味道确实不太好闻。","id":111,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":112},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"那就好，是我多虑了。","id":113,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"还有，工匠团刚刚来人问您那把剑的事。","id":114,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......先放着吧。虽然有点遗憾，但那把剑的主人暂时应该不会来取了。","id":116,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1","focus":"1","id":117},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"是。那么筹备工作已经全部完成了，只待明天剪彩仪式开始。","id":118,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":119},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"既然你过来了，就在这里坐一会儿吧，正好我也想听听你对这次行动的看法。","id":120,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":121},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"遵命。","id":122,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"......但我只是一名普通的年轻骑士，资历尚浅，或许没有什么值得您重视的见解......","id":123,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":124},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"没关系，我最初被前任骑士团长要求潜入莱塔尼亚的时候，也只是一名普通的年轻骑士。","id":125,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#3$1","focus":"2","id":126},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"你在这次行动中，亲自执行的任务最多，所见的也最多，还有谁的想法会比你的更有价值呢？","id":127,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":128},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"再说，如今你可是马雷克家族的长骑，不该以普通的骑士自谦吧？","id":129,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":130},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"......感谢您的信任。","id":131,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"马雷克家族向来以培养真正的战士为荣。加入征战骑士的年月里，我尚未有机会为家徽带去荣光，实在惭愧。","id":132,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"......恕我冒昧，请问您呢？这些年我们都从没听您提起过。","id":133,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":134},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"我啊......嗯，也对，骑士之间的确应该聊这些。不过，那个家族的名字已经消失了有些年头了。","id":135,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":136},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"抱歉，是我失言，我不该打听......","id":137,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":138},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"没关系，随意聊一聊嘛。","id":139,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"以前我也生活在这一带。","id":140,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......我还是个孩子的时候，茨沃涅克还在边境附近游弋，与莱塔尼亚的城市警惕地对视。","id":141,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#3$1","focus":"2","id":142},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"晴天的时候，庞大的影子掠过原野。将要成为骑士的孩子们扮演战役中的名将，为谁的木枪先戳中对方而争吵不休。","id":143,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"那或许就是我的思乡之情吧。","id":144,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#3$1","focus":"1","id":145},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"那后来......是主家的骑士战死了吗？","id":146,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":147},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"也不是。那些骑士犯下的是叛国的罪行。","id":148,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":149},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"啊......","id":150,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"当时我只是一名家臣的儿子，年纪还小，没什么身份地位可言。家族私下与莱塔尼亚勾结一事暴露之后，监正会就收回了贵族封号。","id":152,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":153},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"啊，您说的是......无光骑士的传说？帕伦尼斯科家族作为背叛者的主谋，纠集十余名高阶征战骑士，却在密谋之夜遭人诛杀......","id":154,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"不过，这其中应该有夸大其词的成分吧。哪里有人能独身对抗那么多骑士，何况还有莱塔尼亚的术师在场？","id":155,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#3$1","focus":"2","id":156},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"无光“骑士”啊......呵呵。","id":157,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":158},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"虽然我求过那位闯进宴会的年轻游侠手下留情，但他确实没有放过参与阴谋的任何一个人。","id":159,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"那桩丑闻如今已成定论，应该也没什么不能提及的了。","id":160,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":161},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......你们推举我接任骑士团长的时候，老团长原本是不认可的，对吧？","id":162,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#15$1","focus":"2","id":163},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"因为他知道当初我没有选择拼死保护家族的阴谋，而是选择了向人求助，试图阻止这一切。","id":164,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#15$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":165},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"用他的话来说，正义高于忠诚......对于一名征战骑士来说，其实是颇为致命的缺陷。","id":166,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"你对此......又作何想法呢？","id":167,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":168},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":169},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":170},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","id":171},{"type":"Background","image":"31_g5_mini12_village_n","screenadapt":"showall","id":172},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":173},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":174},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","text":"","id":175},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":176},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"当时的事，我也只是听你们说起过。","id":177,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"那小子带着他的朋友们找过来的时候，兄弟们私下里嘀咕，没想到你这贵族公子哥还真有点本事。","id":178,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":179},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"我们甚至还打了个赌。","id":180,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":181},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"既然你粉碎莱塔尼亚阴谋这件事是真的，那“临光家次子欠下巨额赌债被战争英雄西里尔逐出家门”会不会也是真的。","id":182,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":183},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"啊，别在意，我们也赌切斯柏什么时候能把花环编好，送给他红发的库兰塔。","id":184,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":185},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"......或者你们什么时候能改掉把人想得太好的毛病。","id":186,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":187},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......以前他是什么样的人都不重要。","id":188,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"他现在的谋划已经以众多无辜者的性命为代价......如果你拿到的合同属实。","id":189,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":190},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"这是那个大骑士领来的小律师亲自提供的材料，恐怕造不了假。","id":191,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":192},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......","id":193,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#13$1","focus":"2","id":194},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"说实话，我们也没想到能运气这么好，她自己主动把资料都交出来了。","id":195,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#13$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"本来呢，我们是打算稍微威胁一下她，来拿到这些证据......还差点被你搅局了，对吧？","id":196,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#13$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"至于资料本身，恐怕谁也没想到它的重要性。","id":197,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#13$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":198},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"按照转交者的说法，她大概只是想拿法律开个小玩笑，就像我们也只是接到垒石村的村民求助，才打算顺路帮个小忙。","id":199,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"只有切斯柏挺在乎这件事的，为了不让我从她那里问话，甚至做到了借调查之名扣押赏金猎人这一步......","id":200,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"这只能说明，这些由小马雷克签字的合同，与他的家族无关。那家伙背后就是骑士团。","id":201,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":202},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......盖尔工业则是按照要求，招募感染者，出面打点媒体，把袭击事件炒足热度。","id":203,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"然后一手造成了眼下感染者暴动的局面。","id":204,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":205},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"我原本还以为，我跟那小子的关系，至少值得他直接点来问我想法。再怎么说，我的兄弟们可比他找的那些感染者手稳多了。","id":206,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":207},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"不知道那些商人们在给自己的子公司打广告时想过没有，征战骑士究竟能从中获得什么好处？","id":208,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":209},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......做到这个地步，不会只为引发公众恐慌，效仿前不久“银枪天马”进入大骑士领的举动。","id":210,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":211},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"单纯的耀武扬威毫无价值。","id":212,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":213},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"以茨沃涅克的传统，征战骑士想要获得入城借口也不必这么大费周章。","id":214,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#13$1","focus":"2","id":215},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"是啊，如果是为了这种事，他也不用把你的剑拿走了。","id":216,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#13$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":217},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"......顺带，他倒是对我提过，想为瑟莉娜的事复仇。","id":218,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":219},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......这件事上，我没必要对他解释。","id":220,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":221},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"哈，他当然不是只针对你，但我猜他跟你约定还剑的时间，多半有个原因。","id":222,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":223},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......","id":224,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"明天有一场剪彩仪式。","id":225,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":226},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"真巧，我也在考虑这件事。","id":227,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#13$1","focus":"2","id":228},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"要么是那个时候他的事情都办完了，省得你插手，要么是有什么事要开始了，他希望你动手。","id":229,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#13$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":230},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"最坏的可能呢，就是二者都有。比如......让你看着那个莱塔尼亚人死在象征两国友好的雕塑前面。","id":231,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":232},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"够了......他不该这样。","id":233,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":234},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-50","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":235},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":236},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"等等，你要去哪？","id":237,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":238},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"他不该被任何东西冲昏头脑，更不该选择下作手段。","id":239,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"我去找他谈谈。","id":240,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":241},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":242},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":243},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","id":244},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_coldforest","screenadapt":"showall","id":245},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":246},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":247},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","text":"","id":248},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":249},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......哎，抱歉，我好像问了个难为人的问题。","id":250,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#3$1","focus":"2","id":251},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"我只是在想，如果今晚行动目标意外出现在贫民区，真的是出于你听到的那些堪称天真烂漫的理由......","id":252,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"还能怀有那种理想的人，在我看来是不该死的，即使这个时代最先吞噬的就是他们。","id":253,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":254},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"呵呵......你为什么认同这次行动？","id":255,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":256},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"此次行动，骑士团上下一心。","id":257,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"我们都认为，那些被包裹在城市的茧之中做着美梦的人们，是时候面对现实的斗争与迫在眉睫的威胁了。","id":258,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"莱塔尼亚人膨胀的野心已经初现端倪，战争筹备片刻不曾停歇。既然他们已经预备撕开和平的面纱，我们不该一味受制于人。","id":259,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"退一步来说，即使此次事件并未引燃卡西米尔与莱塔尼亚的冲突，民众也会记住这段惶惶不安的时日。","id":260,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"他们会明白，真正有能力保护他们的人在哪里。","id":261,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":262},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"啊，我做动员讲话的时候就是这么说的吧？","id":263,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":264},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"呃，抱歉......只是，这也确实是大家的想法。","id":265,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"......要说另外还有什么的话......战场也是骑士真正能够建功立业的地方。","id":266,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"我们只是驻扎边远地区的普通骑士团，既无煊赫战绩，也没有悠久的历史，规模也只能算中规中矩。","id":267,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"当然，我们这些人大都是骑士家族的附庸或家臣，没有天马的优秀血统或者名门出身，本来也难以跻身几支核心骑士团。","id":268,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"但如果真有踏上战场的机会，我们一定会证明自己。我们不会任由商人将我们的胜利转卖，也不会在敌人的炮火前畏缩。","id":269,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"......愿所有卡西米尔人如今仍有这样的信念。","id":270,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":271},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"不，不要这么说......战争本来就是我们骑士的职责。","id":272,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"他们可以软弱，也可以恐惧，我们替他们打仗，让他们相信我们。","id":273,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#11$1","focus":"2","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"咳......","id":275,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#11$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#11$1","focus":"1","id":276},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"呃，风向变了，您要不坐到这边来？别被烟熏到眼睛。","id":277,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":278},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"没事。","id":279,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":280},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"......您在烧的是......瑟莉娜队长的笔记？","id":281,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":282},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"嗯。不用担心，看了这么多遍，内容大致已经记住了。","id":283,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"只是近几年边境的变化不小，许多记录已经不再适用，我想早些处理掉，以免成为将来的桎梏。","id":284,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":285},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"......您说得对。如今我们还是很想念她。","id":286,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"您应该也知道，我们对监正会失望的原因之一，就是那次贵族之间的斗争。","id":287,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"那样一座小村庄的地产归属纷争，竟然让队长成了牺牲品。","id":288,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":289},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"不，其实事情的真相并不是什么复杂的政治斗争。","id":290,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":291},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......当然，那些最终害死她的人，我和你们一样不会忘记。","id":292,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":293},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"那些人只是等了很多年，终于等到了一个报复我们的机会。","id":294,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"在加入征战骑士的队伍之前，我们得罪过不少有头有脸的人物。他们为警示我不要轻举妄动......就这么拿她的性命做代价。","id":295,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":296},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"抱歉，我并不是有意打听......","id":297,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":298},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"这本来就是应该堂堂正正提起的事情。","id":299,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":300},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"我们只是希望帮助那些受税金重压而食不果腹的人，被商业联合会的工程车队推平家园的人......","id":301,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":302},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"为那些人的境遇感到难过，才是人之常情。","id":303,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":304},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"我们所做的事情绝无不光彩之处，是大贵族和商人们让新闻和自己一起保持了沉默，试图掩盖累累罪行。","id":305,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"我想，至少在骑士之间，这种沉默是不应该存在的......","id":306,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":307},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"骑士不该向权贵低头，但值得向他人的苦难下跪。","id":308,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":309},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"......如果日后还有机会，我会尝试着去践行。","id":310,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":311},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"在如今的卡西米尔，暂时还很难。","id":312,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":313},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"大多数在此寻求理想的人，后来都会发现自己并非面对着平原坦途，而只是在悬崖边战战兢兢，勉强立足。","id":314,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":315},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"那些以死志投身深渊的人，你甚至听不见一点他们的回响。","id":316,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......因此我才试图以战争的雷霆叩问大地，希望在绝地中开出道路。","id":317,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":318},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":319},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":320},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#9$1","id":321},{"type":"Background","image":"31_g5_mini12_village_n","screenadapt":"showall","id":322},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":323},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":324},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":325},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"找他？你打算去哪里找他？征战骑士的驻地？","id":326,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":327},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"不然呢？","id":328,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":329},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"我给他写过信了，如果真有什么该说的，我算是都说过啦。只是事到如今，咱们还能不能劝他回头，我可就不知道了。","id":330,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":331},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......这件事没有静观其变的余地，托兰。","id":332,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":333},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"我不可能看着他把所有的希望赌在战争上。那和承认自己失败有什么区别？","id":334,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":335},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"......是啊，就是因为失望透顶，才会想到最极端的出路。我们能理解这一点，才会愤怒不已。","id":336,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"不是冲着他......是冲着这个把我们都逼得走投无路的卡西米尔。","id":337,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"但就算你真想对抗一整个骑士团，也真的有那个本事......他拿走你的剑，就是为了这种情况。","id":338,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":339},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"我难道能不去劝阻他？","id":340,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":341},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"——以前猎人们为什么愿意跟着你走？","id":342,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":343},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......","id":344,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":345},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"你没必要跟征战骑士作对。","id":346,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":347},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"你也没必要这么意气用事。","id":348,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":349},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"当然啦，我知道你在顾虑什么。","id":350,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"那几位猎人兄弟确实还在骑士们的手里，有些事办起来没那么方便。跟征战骑士硬碰硬，我们也没什么胜算。","id":351,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#13$1","focus":"2","id":352},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"但切斯柏他一个人自作主张，就已经挺让人伤心的啦。我至少可以期望，你们骑士老爷别都是一个德行吧？","id":353,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#13$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#13$1","focus":"1","id":354},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......","id":355,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":356},{"type":"Dialog","id":357},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":358},{"type":"Character","id":359},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":360},{"type":"Background","image":"31_g3_mini12_farmland","screenadapt":"showall","id":361},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":362},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":363},{"type":"Text","text":"我不喜欢父亲的想法。是谁决定了自己是耕作者，而他人是需要栽培的作物？","id":364},{"type":"Text","text":"是谁决定了自己可以将作物翻进土地，为了这片土壤变得更加肥沃？","id":365},{"type":"Text","text":"......不，我不会把这些写进回信的。骑士不应该一味质疑，却找不到值得坚信的答案。","id":366},{"type":"Text","text":"但我会一直记得这些疑问的声音。","id":367},{"type":"Dialog","id":368},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":369},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":370},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":371},{"type":"Background","image":"31_g5_mini12_village_n","screenadapt":"showall","id":372},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#13$1","id":373},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":374},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":375},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":376},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"......放心，你现在要还是想自己去找那家伙聊聊，我是不会再拦你的，最多只会感叹一句关系生疏啦。","id":377,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":378},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"只是你该好好想想。","id":379,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_008","id":380},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赏金猎人","text":"老大。","id":381,"figure":"avg_npc_008"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","id":382},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"有急事？","id":383,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_008","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":384},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赏金猎人","text":"嗯。那位莱塔尼亚的贵族带着侍卫，悄悄出发了。","id":385,"figure":"avg_npc_008"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_008","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":386},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"现在？","id":387,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","id":388},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"他们想在这时候逃离卡西米尔？......不切实际。","id":389,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"征战骑士不会错过他们的行踪。","id":390,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_625_1#7$1","id":391},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"哎，看来我们没多少商量的时间啦。","id":392,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"原本我来这里也是想找几个刚接触的合作伙伴见见面，所以出事之前，我至少得先去联络一下他们。让他们死在这场风波里可不划算。","id":393,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":394},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......","id":395,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":396},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"托兰，我有生意要谈。","id":397,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":398},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"保护那个莱塔尼亚人......","id":399,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":400},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"......行啊。","id":401,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":402},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"随便我们用什么方法，只要阻止征战骑士第一时间的行动，对吧？","id":403,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"那就还是老样子，我按我的规矩办事。","id":404,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":405},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"你呢？","id":406,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":407},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"我还是会去见切斯柏。","id":408,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":409},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"哈。","id":410,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"但凡你觉得是正确的事情，你就没回过头，更别说衡量值不值得了。","id":411,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":412},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"那么......最后一个问题。","id":413,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"——你不会真的只打算去谈谈，对吧？","id":414,"figure":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":415},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......","id":416,"figure":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":417},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":418},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4064_mlynar_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_625_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":419},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":420},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":421},{"type":"Character","id":422},{"type":"Image","image":"31_mini12_i5","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","fadetime":"0","id":423},{"type":"ImageTween","xFrom":"-30","xTo":"30","duration":"50","xScaleFrom":"1.2","yScaleFrom":"1.2","xScaleTo":"0.85","yScaleTo":"0.85","block":"false","id":424},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":425},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":426},{"type":"Text","text":"夜风裹挟的寒意令人战栗，一片漆黑中，只有河水急促奔流的声音传来。","id":427},{"type":"Text","text":"河谷那一边，工厂静静矗立，灯火映照出它庞大的钢铁身躯。","id":428},{"type":"Text","text":"人们还相信自己能追回落日的时刻，血与火皆有热度的时刻，他们脚下曾有一段很长的路。","id":429},{"type":"Text","text":"如今却没有留给他们片刻回想的时间。","id":430},{"type":"Text","text":"对这面目全非的往昔，无论怀念或是恼怒，都来不及涌上心头。","id":431},{"type":"Text","text":"玛恩纳向他伸出手。","id":432},{"type":"Text","text":"“——给我一把剑吧。”","id":433},{"type":"Dialog","id":434},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":435},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":436},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":437},{"type":"Image","id":438},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","id":439},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_coldforest","screenadapt":"showall","id":440},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":441},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"$darkness01_loop","volume":"0.6","id":442,"musicid":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":443},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","text":"","id":444},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":445},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"是的，目标正处于前往移动城市出口的高速路上。","id":446,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":447},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"他竟然胆怯到不顾第二天的仪式......这件事本身也要给双方的外交关系蒙上阴影。","id":448,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":449},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"是否需要我们接管城市出入口，阻止目标离开？","id":450,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":451},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......","id":452,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#15$1","focus":"2","id":453},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"还有其他人在监视目标吗？","id":454,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#15$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#15$1","focus":"1","id":455},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"......附近只有两名睡在大街长椅上的流浪汉。","id":456,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":457},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"先以安全检查为由，控制游客出入口。","id":458,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":459},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"遵命。","id":460,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":461},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":462},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"1","id":463},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":464},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":465},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"......抱歉，请您稍等。","id":466,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"有传令兵带来的紧急命令。","id":467,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":468},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"切斯柏","text":"......","id":469,"figure":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_627_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":470},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"是......大骑士长亲自签署的调令。","id":471,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"征战骑士","text":"她要求我们整支骑士团即刻调离茨沃涅克，前往大骑士领报到。","id":472,"figure":"avg_npc_624_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":473},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":474},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":475},{"type":"Character","id":476},{"type":"Image","id":477}],"characters":["托兰","玛恩纳","泽诺","征战骑士","切斯柏","赏金猎人"]}